title: NHK Great Nature 2014 Amazing Works of Light in the Sky Mongolia
description: Amazing Works of Light in the Sky: Mongolia Nature Documentary hosted by Akinori Arai, published by NHK broadcasted as part of NHK Great Nature series in 2014 - English narration. http://docuwiki.net/images/0/0d/Amazing-Works-of-Light-in-the-Sky-Mongolia-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ Amazing Works of Light in the Sky: Mongolia. We present the amazing phenomena created by ice and light in the super-cold air of the winter plains, including double and triple suns and light pillars.
